Program: Outlook
Title: Bernard Baran Gets a Retrial
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbs6y
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
Bernard Baran, jailed 21 years ago on child abuse charge who has always claimed his innocence gets a retrial. Also, a new deal for young mothers who live on the streets in Cairo; An interview with transgender pioneer April Ashley; A soundscape from the streets of New York. Presenter: Heather Payton